data.description: Ranchette sit on a fenced 41,382 SF lot with domestic water well plus a contiguous fenced lot 53,130 SF APN#352-060-10 with a domestic water well that requires equipment. Asphalt frontage makes ingress and egrees easy for horses, toy trailer and RV. This home has been upgraded with interior tile flooring, paint, windows, doors, plumbing fixtures. The kitchen has been completely renovated with new cabinets, quartz countertops, wood look ceramic tile plank flooring, new farm sink and appliances. there is new over head lighting fixtures and fans. There is electric heater, wood burning fireplace with blower, evaporative & refrigerated air conditioning units. The roof is newer and in good condition. There are 3 horse stalls with shades and water. Both properties are fenced secured
